videos.description: With time winding down, Miami's Sheldon McClellan rushes down the court and throws up a jumper to beat the buzzer at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Hurricanes heave it up at the buzzer

videos.description: On the outlet pass, Miami's Angel Rodriguez throws it up to Davon Reed for the dunk that ignites the crowd and the broadcasters.
